<edge source="concept.abstinence" target="concept.food" id="edge.food_drink.concept.abstinence.concerns_food.concept.food">
  <data key="d6">edge.food_drink.concept.abstinence.concerns_food.concept.food</data>
  <data key="d7">ssion departs from the good of reason , there is need of a special virtue . Now pleasures of the table are of a nature to withdraw man from the good of reason , both because they are so great, and because food is necessary to man who needs it for the maintenance of life, which he d</data>
  <data key="d8">concept.food</data>
  <data key="d9">Food</data>
  <data key="d10">object</data>
